	<article class="post-21414 post type-post status-publish hentry category-featured-posts tag-afghanistan tag-caracol-haiti tag-coca-plant tag-cocaine-and-crack-cocaine tag-colombia tag-drug-abuse-and-traffic tag-extradition tag-house-of-representatives tag-international-relations tag-netflix-inc tag-nineteen-hundred-nineties tag-obama-barack tag-revolutionary-armed-forces-of-colombia tag-senate tag-state-department tag-television tag-united-states tag-united-states-international-relations tag-united-states-politics-and-government per-obama-barack des-coca-plant des-cocaine-and-crack-cocaine des-drug-abuse-and-traffic des-extradition des-international-relations des-nineteen-hundred-nineties des-television des-united-states-international-relations des-united-states-politics-and-government org-house-of-representatives org-netflix-inc org-revolutionary-armed-forces-of-colombia org-senate org-state-department geo-afghanistan geo-caracol-haiti geo-colombia geo-united-states news_keywords-1990s news_keywords-afghanistan news_keywords-barack-obama news_keywords-caracol-haiti news_keywords-coca news_keywords-cocaine-and-crack news_keywords-colombia news_keywords-drug-abuse news_keywords-extradition news_keywords-farc news_keywords-house-of-representatives news_keywords-international-relations-2 news_keywords-netflix news_keywords-senate news_keywords-state-department news_keywords-tv news_keywords-us news_keywords-us-foreign-policy news_keywords-us-politics" id="post-21414">
